    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1875-01-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1875-01-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="112" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d112">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Foster</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Sutter</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-01-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi>
                            28</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">John A. Sutter</hi>,<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">American Consul, Acapulco:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The government will furnish Mr. Hutchinson a guard, if he desires to return
                        by land.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>JOHN W. FOSTER.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
